headline: Parker-Hannifin (PH): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Parker-Hannifin trades at $735.30 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 11.3% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 8.1%.
